<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" ><generator uri="https://jekyllrb.com/" version="4.1.1">Jekyll</generator><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml" rel="self" type="application/atom+xml" /><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" /><updated>2021-10-13T21:25:30+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/feed.xml</id><title type="html">Hermosawave Photography</title><subtitle>A series of daily landscape photographs by Daniel Sofer, over 18 years running.</subtitle><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><entry><title type="html">Kyoto City Hall・京都市役所</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211013/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kyoto City Hall・京都市役所" /><published>2021-10-13T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-10-13T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/city-hall</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211013/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
The 1927 Kyoto City Hall  building, recently reopened after a several year long renovation.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
1927年に建てられた京都市役所は、数年に及ぶ改修工事を経て、最近リニューアルオープンしました。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">The 1927 Kyoto City Hall building, recently reopened after a several year long renovation.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2110_A7R01148.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Purple Berries・紫ベリー</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211012/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Purple Berries・紫ベリー" /><published>2021-10-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-10-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/berries</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211012/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Purple Beautyberries on a rainy day at Tenryuji Temple. In Japanese, their name is &quot;Murasaki Shikibu,&quot; named after the author of &lt;em&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Tale_of_Genji&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;The Tale of Genji&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
雨降った朝で、天龍寺に「紫式部」のベリーを見ます。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Flowers" /><category term="Tenryu-ji" /><summary type="html">Purple Beautyberries on a rainy day at Tenryuji Temple. In Japanese, their name is &quot;Murasaki Shikibu,&quot; named after the author of The Tale of Genji.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2110_IMG_4431.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Arashiyama Sunrise・嵐山の日出</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211010/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Arashiyama Sunrise・嵐山の日出" /><published>2021-10-10T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-10-10T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211010/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Sun rises over the Togetsu Bridge. A heron stands on a rock looking for breakfast (center), while ducks feed on bread crumbs tossed by local residents off-camera to the left.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
渡月橋から昇る太陽。岩の上で朝食を探すサギ（中）と、カメラの外で住民が投げたパンくずを食べるカモ（左）。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html">Sun rises over the Togetsu Bridge. A heron stands on a rock looking for breakfast (center), while ducks feed on bread crumbs tossed by local residents off-camera to the left.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2110_A7R01123-HDR.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Twilight on the Bay・湾のトワイライト</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211008/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Twilight on the Bay・湾のトワイライト" /><published>2021-10-08T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-10-08T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kobe</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211008/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Above, looking southwest at the city of Kobe and the Osaka Bay from Mt. Rokko. The islands of Shikoku and Awaji are in the distance. Below, looking southeast at more of Kobe, with Osaka in the distance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
上の写真は、六甲山から神戸の街と大阪湾を眺める。 遠くには四国や淡路島が見える。下、南東方向に神戸を眺め。遠くに大阪を見ています。
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;subimagegroup&quot;&gt;
         &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/2021/2110_A7R01043.jpg&quot;/&gt;   
    &lt;/div&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Water" /><summary type="html">Above, looking southwest at the city of Kobe and the Osaka Bay from Mt. Rokko. The islands of Shikoku and Awaji are in the distance. Below, looking southeast at more of Kobe, with Osaka in the distance.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2110_A7R01028.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Morning Rays・朝の日差し</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211007/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Morning Rays・朝の日差し" /><published>2021-10-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-10-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/rays</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211007/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Sun rises over the Katsura River in Arashiyama. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
嵐山の桂川から昇る太陽。


&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Sunrise" /><category term="Katsura River" /><summary type="html">Sun rises over the Katsura River in Arashiyama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2110_A7R00939-HDR.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Sky Painting・空の絵</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211005/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Sky Painting・空の絵" /><published>2021-10-05T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-10-05T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/painting</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211005/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Sun sets behind the mountains, putting on a light show at the Togetsu Bridge in Arashiyama.
 &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
嵐山の渡月橋では、山の向こうにカラフルな空が見えます。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><summary type="html">Sun sets behind the mountains, putting on a light show at the Togetsu Bridge in Arashiyama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2110_A7R00841-HDR.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Fusuma at Daikaku-ji・大覚寺の襖</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211002/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Fusuma at Daikaku-ji・大覚寺の襖" /><published>2021-10-02T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-10-02T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/daikakuji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211002/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Beautiful sumi ink paintings on the fusuma sliding doors at Daikaku-ji temple. Also a few more shots of the temple grounds.
 &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
大覚寺の襖には美しい墨絵があります。また、他にも寺周辺の写真があります。
&lt;/p&gt;

