Early morning in the vast central hall of Kyoto Station.
 &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
京都駅の中央ホールの早朝。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Trains" /><summary type="html">Early morning in the vast central hall of Kyoto Station.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2109_A7R00703.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">River Dawn・川の夜明け</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210925/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="River Dawn・川の夜明け" /><published>2021-09-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-09-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama-dawn</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210925/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Early dawn over the boats docked at the Togetsu Bridge in Arashiyama.
 &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;  
嵐山の渡月橋に停泊している船に夜明け。

&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Dawn" /><category term="Boats" /><summary type="html">Early dawn over the boats docked at the Togetsu Bridge in Arashiyama.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2109_A7R00585.jpg" /></entry></feed>